  "task_html": "<div class=\"task-block task-blue\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Info: Geradengleichung aus zwei Punkten</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 6px 0;\">Vorgehen in 3 Schritten:</p>\n  <ol style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;padding-left:20px;\">\n    <li>Steigung berechnen: <span style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;\">m = (y&#x2082;&minus;y&#x2081;) &divide; (x&#x2082;&minus;x&#x2081;)</span></li>\n    <li>In y = mx + b einsetzen (einen Punkt nutzen)</li>\n    <li>b ausrechnen</li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;margin-top:8px;background:#dbeafe;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 12px;\"><strong>Beispiel</strong> P&#x2081;(0|2), P&#x2082;(3|8):<br>m = (8&minus;2)/(3&minus;0) = 2 &rarr; y = 2x + b<br>P&#x2081; einsetzen: 2 = 2&middot;0 + b &rarr; b = 2 &rarr; <strong>y = 2x + 2</strong></p>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:14px 0 8px 0;\"><strong>Aufgabe:</strong> Bestimme m und b.</p>\n\n<div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n  <table>\n    <thead><tr><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">P&#x2081;</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">P&#x2082;</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">m</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">b</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">(0|1)</td><td class=\"given\">(1|4)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"3\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"1\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">(0|&minus;2)</td><td class=\"given\">(2|2)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-2\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">(1|5)</td><td class=\"given\">(3|1)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-2\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"7\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n      <tr><td class=\"given\">(2|3)</td><td class=\"given\">(6|5)</td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.5\" placeholder=\"m\"></td><td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2\" placeholder=\"b\"></td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkStation(6)\">&#x2713; &#xDC;berpr&#xFC;fen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetStation(6)\">&#x21BA; Zur&#xFC;cksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-6\"></span>\n</div>",
  "sol_html": "<div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:2.2;\">\n  P&#x2081;(0|1), P&#x2082;(1|4): m=(4&minus;1)/1=<strong>3</strong>, b=<strong>1</strong> &rarr; y=3x+1<br>\n  P&#x2081;(0|&minus;2), P&#x2082;(2|2): m=(2&minus;(&minus;2))/2=<strong>2</strong>, b=<strong>&minus;2</strong> &rarr; y=2x&minus;2<br>\n  P&#x2081;(1|5), P&#x2082;(3|1): m=(1&minus;5)/2=<strong>&minus;2</strong>, b=5&minus;(&minus;2&middot;1)=<strong>7</strong> &rarr; y=&minus;2x+7<br>\n  P&#x2081;(2|3), P&#x2082;(6|5): m=(5&minus;3)/4=<strong>0,5</strong>, b=3&minus;0,5&middot;2=<strong>2</strong> &rarr; y=0,5x+2\n</div>"
}
